nger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cThe wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHow is that?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28899,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/taraweeh-prayer-in-ramadan-rakaat\/","url_meta":{"origin":3205,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tarawih: The Prophet\u2019s night prayer in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: He asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cHow was the night prayer of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, during Ramadan?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cHe would not pray more than eleven cycles in Ramadan or other times. He would pray four cycles,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31867,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/believers-paradise-beautiful\/","url_meta":{"origin":3205,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Believers enter Paradise as young, beautiful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people of Paradise will enter Paradise with smooth and hairless skin, kohl upon their eyes, at thirty or thirty-three year